Dialogue: 0,0:04:23.58,0:04:26.22,Default,,0,0,0,,The HQ building is gonna fall!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.36,0:04:33.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Leave your post!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.49,0:04:35.73,Default,,0,0,0,,We're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.16,0:04:42.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this for real?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.37,0:04:47.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody please tell me I'm dreaming!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:48.04,0:04:51.81,Default,,0,0,0,,For centuries we've kept watch\Nover the seas from here!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:51.81,0:04:56.15,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't believe the fort of justice the Navy's citadel...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:56.91,0:04:59.32,Default,,0,0,0,,...is crumbling before my eyes!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.62,0:05:11.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Blackbeard, the one who caught Ace\Nand caused this war,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.06,0:05:13.73,Default,,0,0,0,,now has Whitebeard's power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.73,0:05:17.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Look, all you people of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.20,0:05:20.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Behold me and my power!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:25.44,0:05:28.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What's gonna happen to this world?!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:51.50,0:05:57.47,Default,,0,0,0,,I can feel the power coursing through my body!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.08,0:05:59.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Dammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.24,0:06:04.68,Default,,0,0,0,,What power! It feels like the entire world\Nis in the palm of my hand!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.68,0:06:06.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Bastard!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:11.39,0:06:13.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, what's wrong?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.99,0:06:18.50,Default,,0,0,0,,What are you waiting for? Doesn't anyone wanna fight?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:18.50,0:06:24.00,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm willing to fight you\Nto your hearts' content now! What a shame!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.80,0:06:28.31,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no choice.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.01,0:06:31.38,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's start with...
Dialogue: 0,0:06:31.98,0:06:35.88,Default,,0,0,0,,...sinking Marineford into the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:37.38,0:06:38.62,Default,,0,0,0,,What did he say?!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:58.40,0:07:00.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Shock Wave!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.42,0:07:16.65,Default,,0,0,0,,A building can easily be rebuilt!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.52,0:07:26.93,Default,,0,0,0,,But the island of Marineford\Nis the hub of the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:28.40,0:07:29.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Fleet Admiral!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.60,0:07:35.41,Default,,0,0,0,,To all the citizens of the world,\Nwho fear the villains that roam the seas,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.14,0:07:40.31,Default,,0,0,0,,it is important that we are here!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:42.58,0:07:46.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice and righteousness will never perish!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:46.18,0:07:50.99,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you dare speak lightly of sinking this island,
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.99,0:07:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,you little punk!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.00,0:08:06.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Such noble beliefs! Huh? Fleet Admiral-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:07.14,0:08:08.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, then:
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.37,0:08:13.21,Default,,0,0,0,,defend this place—if you can!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:25.86,0:08:26.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:28.73,0:08:34.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up and get the ship to shore!\NWe can't leave anyone behind!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.43,0:08:37.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait for us! We're coming now!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.84,0:08:42.64,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta get out of here alive!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:42.64,0:08:44.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Hurry up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.08,0:08:52.42,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy's victory must be absolute!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.42,0:08:56.79,Default,,0,0,0,,We gotta survive and leave here as Pops told us to!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.79,0:09:02.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Let the pirates know\Nthe power of justice through fear!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:02.83,0:09:04.69,Default,,0,0,0,,Justice...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.69,0:09:06.40,Default,,0,0,0,,...Through fear...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:06.40,0:09:08.27,Default,,0,0,0,,We're almost there!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:08.27,0:09:13.70,Default,,0,0,0,,That's right! Now is the chance\Nto let villains all over the world know!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.34,0:09:16.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Our power that will...!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:16.47,0:09:18.31,Default,,0,0,0,,...save the world!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.31,0:09:20.11,Default,,0,0,0,,We're safe now!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.11,0:09:22.71,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.18,0:09:25.18,Default,,0,0,0,,The power of justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.02,0:09:29.22,Default,,0,0,0,,Y-Yellow Monkey!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.06,0:09:42.00,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Now is your chance!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:42.67,0:09:44.43,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Take Straw-boy!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.04,0:09:47.27,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.51,0:09:51.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Inazuma!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.51,0:09:55.85,Default,,0,0,0,,You better stop, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.85,0:09:58.08,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,You pest!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:58.58,0:10:01.18,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Let's finish this up!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:01.85,0:10:04.15,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,I won't let you go any further!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.15,0:10:07.89,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,New Kama Kenpo, 44 Aesthetic Arts:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.89,0:10:09.86,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Laser Surgery Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.65,0:10:34.42,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,My nails melted!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.32,0:10:38.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Emporio Ivankov of the Revolutionary Army!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:39.96,0:10:43.53,Default,,0,0,0,,You use some strange techniques,\Nas the rumors say!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.53,0:10:47.26,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,New Kama Kenpo, 44 Aesthetic Arts:
Dialogue: 0,0:10:47.26,0:10:49.80,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Fat Suctioning Fist!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:52.27,0:10:54.50,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,I like it hot!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.37,0:11:01.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I have no time to play with you guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:19.10,0:11:20.50,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:20.50,0:11:24.60,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,I burned my lips, my lips, my lips...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:25.24,0:11:29.07,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,...or not! Because of my over-applied make-up!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:31.51,0:11:33.58,Default,Ivankov,0,0,0,,Ouch!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.05,0:11:39.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I-Iva-sama!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.65,0:11:45.86,Default,,0,0,0,,You bastards!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.32,0:11:48.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them get away! Shoot!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:54.97,0:12:00.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Isn't this too one-sided?\NThe winner has already been decided...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.70,0:12:03.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Is this really necessary?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:07.88,0:12:11.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Crush them! Completely and utterly!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:12.48,0:12:16.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't ever let them even think of challenging us!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.19,0:12:19.32,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.32,0:12:20.96,Default,,0,0,0,,We'll let them know...!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.52,0:12:23.46,Default,,0,0,0,,...The power of our justice!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.90,0:12:28.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:28.37,0:12:29.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:29.73,0:12:31.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:31.13,0:12:33.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Destroy them!!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:34.27,0:12:36.57,Default,,0,0,0,,What is this?!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:36.94,0:12:38.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:38.64,0:12:43.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe! Hand Dragon's son over to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.82,0:12:50.32,Default,,0,0,0,,I'll have an advantage once we get\Nto the sea! I can outrun him!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.19,0:13:00.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Oh no! It's frozen!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.03,0:13:03.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Blue Pheasant!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.04,0:13:07.84,Default,,0,0,0,,He's coming!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.61,0:13:15.15,Default,,0,0,0,,Looks like you've got nowhere to run!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.48,0:13:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,It's no good!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:21.89,0:13:24.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hat Luffy!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:26.22,0:13:28.59,Default,,0,0,0,,I've got you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:03.39,0:14:04.73,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.47,0:14:13.97,Default,,0,0,0,,It went right through Jinbe and reached Ace's brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:13.97,0:14:15.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Are they still alive?!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:18.74,0:14:20.28,Default,,0,0,0,,I can't let him get hurt anymore!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.48,0:14:30.55,Default,,0,0,0,,You're in my way, Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.43,0:14:50.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Luffy-kun, I'm sorry! I couldn't save you!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:50.87,0:14:54.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool! You should be worrying about yourself right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:03.89,0:15:06.96,Default,,0,0,0,,My aim was a little off because you were in the way.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.62,0:15:11.26,Default,,0,0,0,,If it hit his heart, it would've been easier for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.90,0:15:13.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you think so, Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:20.77,0:15:24.24,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you gonna keep protecting him\Nwith that hole in his chest?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.68,0:15:32.22,Default,,0,0,0,,He's gonna die soon!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.53,0:15:55.74,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe, if I don't escape death...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.81,0:16:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry but could you look after my brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.78,0:16:04.75,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm not helping him because he is your brother!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.15,0:16:07.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I think highly of Luffy-kun!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.18,0:16:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,I've already made up my mind\Nto save his life even if it means my death!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:29.84,0:16:32.48,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let him die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:42.89,0:16:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Even if I die,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:46.39,0:16:49.69,Default,,0,0,0,,I won't let Luffy-kun die!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:54.73,0:16:56.33,Default,,0,0,0,,That's nonsense!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.24,0:17:08.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:08.65,0:17:09.71,Default,,0,0,0,,Sables!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:17.42,0:17:20.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Somebody, catch them and put them on a ship!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:20.66,0:17:21.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:21.76,0:17:23.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Crocodile!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:24.09,0:17:27.50,Default,,0,0,0,,You gotta protect the one you wanna protect!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.50,0:17:31.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't let them have their way!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:32.37,0:17:33.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Catch them!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.51,0:17:37.37,Default,,0,0,0,,It's over!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.37,0:17:40.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry that I got carried away, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:40.78,0:17:43.61,Default,,0,0,0,,This is the end of Captain Buggy's legend.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:43.61,0:17:46.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you for your support this whole time!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:46.62,0:17:48.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:55.49,0:17:57.13,Default,,0,0,0,,They're not coming down...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:58.43,0:18:00.00,Default,,0,0,0,,What's going on?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:00.00,0:18:01.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:02.40,0:18:05.47,Default,,0,0,0,,He helped Straw Hat and Jinbe!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:05.47,0:18:07.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Just as I thought!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.60,0:18:08.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:08.94,0:18:12.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy, you made us\Nbelieve you were gonna run
Dialogue: 0,0:18:12.28,0:18:16.91,Default,,0,0,0,,but you helped your fellow escapee, Straw Hat, when it counted!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.15,0:18:20.15,Default,,0,0,0,,How noble!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.15,0:18:23.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Your nobility is blinding!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.09,0:18:26.66,Default,,0,0,0,,They're being weird again!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:28.66,0:18:30.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Jinbe and Straw Hat!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.56,0:18:37.03,Default,,0,0,0,,How did you end up in the sky, covered in blood?!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.03,0:18:38.90,Default,,0,0,0,,Anyway, why is it so hot here...?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.14,0:18:43.87,Default,,0,0,0,,M-Magma!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:47.01,0:18:51.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, red-nosed man! You helped us!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.05,0:18:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't know what's going on\Nand I'm not helping you!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.92,0:18:57.09,Default,,0,0,0,,But I allowed Luffy-kun to get injured!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:57.09,0:19:01.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He needs to be treated immediately!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.02,0:19:05.16,Default,,0,0,0,,Shut up! I'm the one who needs help, fool!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:07.83,Default,,0,0,0,,How could we get him treated here...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:07.83,0:19:09.97,Default,,0,0,0,,Did you call me "red-nosed man"?!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.43,0:19:13.37,Default,,0,0,0,,They keep getting in my way\Nthe moment I'm about to get him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.37,0:19:15.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Rose Rondo!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.82,0:19:36.79,Default,,0,0,0,,You're fools, one and all!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.79,0:19:40.50,Default,,0,0,0,,Do you wanna die just to save that Straw Hat brat?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:41.26,0:19:47.97,Default,,0,0,0,,We all witnessed\Nhis boundless determination and power.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:47.97,0:19:52.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Ace protected him and Pops acknowledged him!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.98,0:19:56.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Now it's our duty to send him off into the new era!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.01,0:20:01.05,Default,,0,0,0,,I thought all of you were smarter than that!\NNot that it matters!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.33,0:20:14.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Whitebeard Pirates!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:15.16,0:20:16.40,Default,,0,0,0,,Red Hound!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.00,0:20:20.87,Default,,0,0,0,,The fear you see in that boy—\Nthat makes you wanna kill him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:20.87,0:20:25.98,Default,,0,0,0,,The potential we see in him—\Nthat makes us wanna protect him.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:25.98,0:20:28.18,Default,,0,0,0,,They're the same, don't you think?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.18,0:20:32.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You guys got me involved again!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.18,0:20:34.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Are you even listening?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:34.92,0:20:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,H-Hey, Jinbe?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:37.95,0:20:43.59,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't tell me that you're unconscious! Where should I go now?!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:43.59,0:20:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:46.56,0:20:50.17,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether he lives or dies,\Nit'll be like he's in hell regardless.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.07,0:20:54.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Might as well make him suffer while he lives!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:55.17,0:20:58.51,Default,,0,0,0,,Discussion is pointless, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:00.68,0:21:01.94,Default,,0,0,0,,So be it!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.06,0:21:17.36,Default,,0,0,0,,W-We're dead!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.93,0:21:20.80,Default,,0,0,0,,It's Sengoku vs. Blackbeard over there.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:28.14,0:21:30.67,Default,,0,0,0,,And it's Red Hound vs. the commanders over here!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:37.75,0:21:40.68,Default,,0,0,0,,The fighting hasn't stopped!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:40.68,0:21:43.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain Buggy! Do something!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:43.82,0:21:46.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Damn it all, fools!
Dialogue: 0,0:21:46.02,0:21:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Give me a break... Honestly!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:13.28,0:22:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Captain, we've reached\Na point where it's not frozen.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:17.75,0:22:19.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Surface.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:28.60,0:22:31.80,Default,,0,0,0,,What is that?! A ship came out of the water!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.44,0:22:34.20,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a submarine!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:34.20,0:22:36.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Is it another enemy?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:37.01,0:22:38.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Whose ship is that?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.31,0:22:42.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Put Straw Hatter on my ship! {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:43.28,0:22:48.58,Default,,0,0,0,,"Straw Hatter"?\NThat sure is a strange way to call somebody! {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:49.15,0:22:50.62,Default,,0,0,0,,Who the hell are you, brat?!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:51.52,0:22:53.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Straw Hatter and I\Nmay become enemies in the future {Straw Hat-ya}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:53.92,0:22:56.03,Default,,0,0,0,,but I have nothing against him.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.03,0:22:58.56,Default,,0,0,0,,There's no point in letting him die here.
