Dialogue: 1,0:22:58.63,0:23:03.37,Sign,,0,0,366,,{\bord0\blur0.6\fad(666,0)\4a&HFF&}Heart Pirates Captain\N{\fnFOT-Greco Std B\fs99\bord0}Trafalgar Law
Dialogue: 0,0:22:59.30,0:23:01.63,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,I'll help him escape!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:01.63,0:23:03.37,DefaultLow,,0,0,0,,Leave him to me!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.37,0:23:04.90,Default,,0,0,0,,W-What?!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:11.34,0:23:13.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm a doctor!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.45,0:23:24.99,Default,,0,0,0,,The Navy's relentless pursuit continues.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.99,0:23:27.62,Default,,0,0,0,,As the meaningless battle rages on endlessly,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:27.62,0:23:29.99,Default,,0,0,0,,one young man stands\Nlost in grief on the battlefield.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.69,0:23:34.26,Default,,0,0,0,,That sadness gives birth\Nto a great power called courage,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:34.26,0:23:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,setting the very world in motion!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.77,0:23:38.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Next time, on One Piece:
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.13,0:23:42.17,Default,,0,0,0,,"A Desperate Scream\NThe Fateful Moment of Courage"
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.17,0:23:44.44,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm gonna be the Pirate King!!
